                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="clearfix">
                        <label class="section-subhd">Risk Management:</label>
                        <p>
                            Risk of harm to learners and employees must be effectively mitigated. This starts at the
                            programme planning stage and carries through programme development and implementation to
                            any debriefing activity that may occur.
                        </p>
